usage: pathfix.py [-h] [-a APPLY] [-l LIST] [-e EXPORT] [-p PREVIEW] [-c]
                  [-i INSTALL]

optional arguments:
  -h, --help  show this help message and exit
  -a APPLY    apply the config to environment variables
  -l LIST     display the current contents of variable
  -e EXPORT   writes current environment variables to config
  -p PREVIEW  parses and prints the config without modifying the environment
  -c          Limit applied changes to current user (Defaults to all users)
  -i INSTALL  apply the config to environment variables on every startup
